approved: true
description: <p>The Cabin font family is a humanist sans \
  with 4 weights and true italics, inspired by Edward \
  Johnston’s and Eric \
  Gill’s typefaces, with a touch of modernism.</p> \
  <p>Cabin incorporates modern proportions, \
  optical adjustments, and some elements \
  of the geometric sans.</p> \
  <p>It remains true to its roots, \
  but has its own personality.</p> \
  <p>The weight distribution is almost monotone, \
  although top and bottom curves are slightly \
  thin.</p> \
  <p>Counters of the b, g, p and q are rounded \
  and optically adjusted. The curved stem \
  endings have a 10 degree angle. E and F \
  have shorter center arms. M is splashed.</p>

# Note: weight values are slightly inconsistent, as original checkin
# used "bold", but additional weights added have numeric values.
font.Cabin-Regular.ttf.weight: 400
font.Cabin-Italic.ttf.weight: 400
font.Cabin-Medium.ttf.weight: 500
font.Cabin-MediumItalic.ttf.weight: 500
font.Cabin-SemiBold.ttf.weight: 600
font.Cabin-SemiBoldItalic.ttf.weight: 600
font.Cabin-Bold.ttf.weight: bold
font.Cabin-BoldItalic.ttf.weight: bold

font.Cabin-Italic.ttf.style: italic
font.Cabin-MediumItalic.ttf.style: italic
font.Cabin-SemiBoldItalic.ttf.style: italic
font.Cabin-BoldItalic.ttf.style: italic
